Package: picreg
Type: Package
Title: Variable Selection using the Pivotal Information Criterion
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2026-05-18
Authors@R: c(
    person("Maxime", "Van Cutsem",
           role  = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "maxime.vancutsem@unige.ch"))
Description: Sparse regression and classification with
    automatic regularisation parameter selection via the Pivotal
    Detection Boundary (PDB) method. Implements FISTA optimisation for
    L1, SCAD and MCP penalties across Gaussian, Binomial, Poisson,
    Exponential, Gumbel and Cox families. The PDB selector chooses the
    regularisation parameter as a quantile of a pivotal null-distribution
    statistic, eliminating the need for cross-validation.
    See <doi:10.48550/arXiv.2603.04172>.
